for i in range(1, 6):
    print('----------------------------------------') ; print(" :", i)
    url = 'https://www.coupang.com/np/search?q=%EB%85%B8%ED%8A%B8%EB%B6%81&channel=recent&component=&eventCategory=SRP&trcid=&traid=&sorter=scoreDesc&minPrice=&maxPrice=&priceRange=&filterType=&listSize=36&filter=&isPriceRange=false&brand=&offerCondition=&rating=0&page={}&rocketAll=false&searchIndexingToken=&backgroundColor='.format(i)
    res = requests.get(url, headers=headers)

    soup = bs(res.text, "html.parser")

    items = soup.find_all("li", attrs={"class":re.compile("^search-product")})

    for item in items:
        #   
        ad_badge = item.find("span", attrs={"class":"ad-badge-text"})

            continue

        if rate:
            rate = rate.get_text()
        else:
            print(" <   > ") ; print()
            continue

        rate_count = item.find("span", attrs={"class":"rating-total-count"}) #  
        if rate_count:
            rate_count = rate_count.get_text()[1:-1]
            # print(" ", rate_count)

headers = {"User-Agent":"Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/92.0.4515.107 Safari/537.36 Edg/92.0.902.55"}

for i in range(1, 6):
    #print('----------------------------------------') ; print(" :", i)
    url = 'https://www.coupang.com/np/search?q=%EB%85%B8%ED%8A%B8%EB%B6%81&channel=recent&component=&eventCategory=SRP&trcid=&traid=&sorter=scoreDesc&minPrice=&maxPrice=&priceRange=&filterType=&listSize=36&filter=&isPriceRange=false&brand=&offerCondition=&rating=0&page={}&rocketAll=false&searchIndexingToken=&backgroundColor='.format(i)
    res = requests.get(url, headers=headers)

    soup = bs(res.text, "html.parser")

    items = soup.find_all("li", attrs={"class":re.compile("^search-product")})

    for item in items:
        #   
        ad_badge = item.find("span", attrs={"class":"ad-badge-text"})
        if ad_badge:
            #print(" <  >") ; print()
            continue

        name = item.find("div", attrs={"class":"name"}).get_text() # 

        #   
        if "Apple" in name:
            #print(" <Apple  > ") ; print()
            continue

        price = item.find("strong", attrs={"class":"price-value"}).get_text() # 

        #  100 ,  4.5    
        rate = item.find("em", attrs={"class":"rating"}) # 
        if rate:
            rate = rate.get_text()
        else:
            #print(" <   > ") ; print()
            continue

        rate_count = item.find("span", attrs={"class":"rating-total-count"}) #  
        if rate_count:
            rate_count = rate_count.get_text()[1:-1]
            # print(" ", rate_count)
        else:
            # print(" <    > ") ; print()
            continue
            
        link = item.find("a", attrs={"class":"search-product-link"})["href"]


        if float(rate) >= 4.5 and int(rate_count) >= 100:
            # print(name) ; print(price) ; print(rate) ; print(rate_count) ; print()
            print(f" : {name}")
            print(f" : {price}")
            print(f" : {rate} ({rate_count})")
            print(" : {}".format("https://www.coupang.com/" + link))
            print("="*70)
